            <h2 class="rule"> The Victoria logo on digital platforms</h2>
            <div class="example"><img alt="" src="/assets/img/logo.png" />
            </div>
            <p>Use the landscape Victoria logo in white on a Victoria green header (Hex: #115737)</p>
            <p>Minimum width of logo should be 190px.</p>
            <p>Always link the Victoria logo back to the victoria.ac.nz home page</p>
            <p>The Victoria word mark logo is strictly for use on mobile responsive applications or pages. No exceptions.</p>

