            <h2 class="rule">Guidance on Victoria colours and fonts</h2>
            <h4>Colours</h4>
			
            <p>The Victoria green should be used sparingly. The Victoria green should only be used as an application header colour and font headings where appropriate.</p>
            <p>Background colour should be white with off-black text (Hex #444).</p>
            <p>Highlight areas should be (Hex #eee) . Border colour is (Hex #b9d2d6). </p>
            <p>Primary Button should be blue with white text, these button should be used for submit or final actions. There are other button styles we use. For more information about buttons see the <a href="/elements#buttons">Victoria elements page</a></p>    
		
